OL,3,CCumbrian school facing closure over
OL,4,CVAT introduction saved by community
OL,6,FLast week Hunter Hall School, in
OL,7,FPenrith, was at risk of closure
OL,8,Ffollowing the government's addition of
OL,9,FVAT to private school fees.
OL,11,FThe primary school launched an
OL,12,Femergency appeal and within just a
OL,13,Fweek it raised more than #180,000.
OL,15,FThe head teacher says they've received
OL,16,F'extraordinary' support from over 350
OL,17,Flocals, parents and those from further
OL,18,Faway.
