OL,3,CCumbrian school facing closure over
OL,4,CVAT introduction saved by community
OL,6,FPaul Burrows said: "We are hugely
OL,7,Fgrateful for, and have been truly
OL,8,Fhumbled by, the warmth and generosity
OL,9,Fshown by our school community, as well
OL,10,Fas the kindness of strangers from
OL,11,Facross the UK.
OL,13,F"We can now look forward to the run up
OL,14,Fto Christmas and being able to enjoy
OL,15,Feverything the final two weeks of term
OL,16,Fhas in store."
OL,18,FAround 80 pupils aged three to 11 make
OL,19,Fup the current cohort, although it's
OL,20,Fsmaller than it's been in its 40-year
OL,21,Fhistory.
