OL,6,FHunter Hall says they have had a
OL,7,Fsignificant impact on their budgets in
OL,8,Frecent years, as larger year groups
OL,9,Fleaving who joined during Covid, and
OL,10,Fcosts for families increasing as VAT
OL,11,Fwas introduced to private school fees.
OL,13,FIt means a reduction in the number of
OL,14,Fstudents studying at the school.
