OL,3,CCumbrian school facing closure over
OL,4,CVAT introduction saved by community
OL,6,FCurrent parent, Sophie Hodgson, said:
OL,7,F"As a parent, I feel a strong sense of
OL,8,Frelief: relief at not having to tell
OL,9,Fmy child she won't be returning to
OL,10,FHunter Hall after Christmas; relief at
OL,11,Fnot having to try and secure a place
OL,12,Fat another primary school weeks before
OL,13,Fthe Christmas break; and relief at
OL,14,Fbeing able to meet the new year
OL,15,Fknowing that the school is on a safe
OL,16,Ffooting for now and the future."
